message("Loading Seurat object...")
## Loading Seurat object...
data.seurat <- readRDS(input_seurat_object)

# Filter only CTRL cells
data.seurat <- data.seurat[,data.seurat$orig.ident == "Pan_neuro_control"]
message(ncol(data.seurat), " cells were loaded")
## 11742 cells were loaded
message(nrow(data.seurat), " genes were loaded")

Plot expression between 2 conditions

# srl = spargel. Also known as dPGC-1, PGC-1α, PGC-1, dPGC1, PGC1-α. FBgn0037248
gene <- "srl"
alias <- "PGC-1α"

#PGC1-alpha, NRF-1 and NRF-2

# Prepare
boxplot_data <- data.frame(expression = data.seurat@assays$RNA@data[gene, ], annotation = data.seurat$annotation_clusters)

# Calculate summary expression per annotation (cluster)
summary_expression <- tapply(boxplot_data$expression, boxplot_data$annotation, mean)

# Sort annotations by mean expression
sorted_annotations <- names(sort(summary_expression, decreasing = TRUE))

# Reorder the annotation factor
boxplot_data$annotation <- factor(boxplot_data$annotation, levels = sorted_annotations)

# Plot
p <- ggplot(boxplot_data, aes(x = annotation, y = expression, fill = annotation)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(x = NULL, y = paste0(gene, " normalized expression\n(",alias,")")) +
  theme_minimal() + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1)) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = annotationClustersPalette) +
  NoLegend()

# Save
ggsave(p, filename = paste0(output_figure_prefix, "ordered_boxplot_",gene,"_CTRL.pdf"), width = 15, height = 5, bg = "white")

gene <- "srl"

data.scatter <- data.frame(srl_expression = data.seurat@assays$RNA@data[gene, ], AUC_OXPHOS_68_Porcelli = data.seurat$AUC_OXPHOS_68_Porcelli)

# Create the scatter plot
p <- ggplot(data.scatter, aes(x = srl_expression, y = AUC_OXPHOS_68_Porcelli)) +
  geom_point() +
  theme_minimal()

# Calculate correlation, p-value, and R²
cor_test <- cor.test(data.seurat@assays$RNA@data[gene, ], data.seurat$AUC_OXPHOS_68_Porcelli, method = "pearson")
cor_value <- cor_test$estimate
p_value <- cor_test$p.value
r_squared <- cor_value^2

# Create the annotation text
annotation_text <- paste("Correlation: ", round(cor_value, 3),
                        "\nP-value: ", format(p_value, scientific = TRUE),
                        "\nR²: ", round(r_squared, 3), sep = "")

# Add the annotation to the plot
p <- p + annotate("text", x = Inf, y = Inf, label = annotation_text, hjust = 1.1, vjust = 1.1, size = 4)

# Save
ggsave(p, filename = paste0(output_figure_prefix, "scatterplot_",gene,"_expression_correlation_CTRL.pdf"), width = 15, height = 5, bg = "white")
ggsave(p, filename = paste0(output_figure_prefix, "scatterplot_",gene,"_expression_correlation_CTRL.png"), width = 15, height = 5, dpi = 1000, bg = 'white')

p

# Create the annotation text
annotation_text <- paste("Correlation: ", round(cor_value, 3),
                        "\nP-value: ", format(p_value, scientific = TRUE),
                        "\nR²: ", round(r_squared, 3), sep = "")

# Add the annotation to the plot
p <- p + annotate("text", x = Inf, y = Inf, label = annotation_text, hjust = 1.1, vjust = 1.1, size = 4)

# Save
ggsave(p, filename = paste0(output_figure_prefix, "scatterplot_",gene,"_expression_correlation_CTRL.pdf"), width = 15, height = 5, bg = "white")

# cnc =     cap-n-collar Also known as Nrf2, CncC, dNrf2, cap and collar, Cap 'n' collar. FBgn0262975 Main ortholog for NRF-2.
gene <- "cnc"
alias <- "NRF-2 ?"

# Prepare
boxplot_data <- data.frame(expression = data.seurat@assays$RNA@data[gene, ], annotation = data.seurat$annotation_clusters)

# Calculate summary expression per annotation (cluster)
summary_expression <- tapply(boxplot_data$expression, boxplot_data$annotation, mean)

# Sort annotations by mean expression
sorted_annotations <- names(sort(summary_expression, decreasing = TRUE))

# Reorder the annotation factor
boxplot_data$annotation <- factor(boxplot_data$annotation, levels = sorted_annotations)

# Plot
p <- ggplot(boxplot_data, aes(x = annotation, y = expression, fill = annotation)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  labs(x = NULL, y = paste0(gene, " normalized expression\n(",alias,")")) +
  theme_minimal() + theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, vjust = 0.5, hjust=1)) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = annotationClustersPalette) +
  NoLegend()

# Save

ggsave(p, filename = paste0(output_figure_prefix, "ordered_boxplot_",gene,"_CTRL.png"), width = 15, height = 5, dpi = 1000, bg = 'white')
